Subject: ext4: Fix deadlock in ext4_write_begin() and ext4_da_write_begin()
To: stable@kernel.org
Cc: "Theodore Ts'o" <tytso@mit.edu>, Ext4 Developers List <linux-ext4@vger.kernel.org>, Jan Kara <jack@suse.cz>
